1969年和其他學院合併形成'''伍爾弗漢普頓理工技校'''（Wolverhampton Polytechnic），有應用科學、藝術設計、文科、工程學和社會科學五個系。<ref name="millennium">{{cite web|url= http://www.wlv.ac.uk/default.aspx?page=21428|title= Looking to the Millennium|accessdate= 2010-01-21|publisher= University of Wolverhampton|archive-date= 2014-07-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140708124739/http://www.wlv.ac.uk/default.aspx?page=21428}}</ref>

1992年獲大學資格並改名為'''伍爾弗漢普頓大學'''（University of Wolverhampton），1994年擴建特爾福德校區

1995年伍爾弗漢普頓科學園開幕，2002年11月改名為伍爾弗漢普頓大學科學園。<ref name="science park">{{cite web |url= http://www.wlv.ac.uk/Default.aspx?page=32948 |title= New name for business park |accessdate= 2013-10-04 |publisher= University of Wolverhampton |archive-date= 2013-12-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131215153225/http://www.wlv.ac.uk/Default.aspx?page=32948 }}</ref>

2000年開始實施翻新計劃，<ref name="Review01">{{cite web |url= http://www2.wlv.ac.uk/annualreview01/intro.html |title= Annual Review 2001 |accessdate= 2010-01-22 |publisher= University of Wolverhampton |archive-date= 2010-01-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100102033149/http://www2.wlv.ac.uk/annualreview01/intro.html }}</ref> 至2010年為止共花費了1.15億英鎊於校園翻新上。<ref name="Review03">{{cite web |url= http://asp.wlv.ac.uk/Level4.asp?UserType=11&Level4=2060 |title= Annual Review 2004:February |accessdate= 2010-01-22 |publisher= University of Wolverhampton |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20051121160357/http://asp.wlv.ac.uk/Level4.asp?UserType=11&Level4=2060 |archivedate= 2005-11-21 }}</ref>

==學術==
===科系===
該大學有七個學術部門：<ref name="schools">{{cite web |url= http://www.wlv.ac.uk/default.aspx?page=6847 |title= Our Schools |accessdate= 2010-02-08 |publisher= University of Wolverhampton |archive-date= 2014-10-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141013044357/http://www.wlv.ac.uk/default.aspx?page=6847 }}</ref>
*藝術設計學院（School of Art and Design）
*未來教育學院（School for Education Futures）
*健康幸福學院（School of Health and Wellbeing）
*法學、社會科學和通信學院（School of Law, Social Sciences and Communications）
*運動、表演藝術和休閒學院（School of Sport, Performing Arts and Leisure）
*伍爾弗漢普頓大學商學院（University of Wolverhampton Business School）
*科學與工程學系（Faculty of Science and Engineering）

===研究===

2008年[[科研評估|科研評估]]將其研究能力評為英國132所機構中的第93位，是英國[[語言學|語言學]]最佳大學之一。<ref name="RAE 2008">[http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/Journals/THE/THE/18_December_2008/attachments/RAE_2008_THE_RESULTS.pdf RAE 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/Journals/THE/THE/18_December_2008/attachments/RAE_2008_THE_RESULTS.pdf |date=20130116101544 }}, ''Times Higher Education Supplement''</ref> 圖書館和信息管理學位居全國第二。<ref name="RAE 2008"/> 其捐款數額也在[[新大學|新大學]]中位居前列。<ref name="rae">{{cite web |url= http://www.wlv.ac.uk/default.aspx?page=21237 |title= Research receives international respect and financial reward |accessdate= 2010-02-05 |publisher= University of Wolverhampton |archive-date= 2014-09-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140906204022/https://www.wlv.ac.uk/Default.aspx?page=21237 }}</ref>

